I"¤<h3 id="start-in-4-steps">Start in 4 steps</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Download or clone repo <code>git clone git@github.com:nandomoreirame/lora.git</code></li>
  <li>Enter the folder: <code>cd lora/</code></li>
  <li>Install Ruby gems: <code>bundle install</code></li>
  <li>Start Jekyll server: <code>jekyll serve</code></li>
</ol>

<p>Access, <a href="http://localhost:4000/">localhost:4000</a></p>

<h3 id="deploy-in-github-pages-in-2-steps">Deploy in Github pages in 2 steps</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Change the variables <code>GITHUB_REPONAME</code> and <code>GITHUB_REPO_BRANCH</code> in
  <code>Rakefile</code></li>
  <li>Run <code>rake</code> or <code>rake publish</code> for build and publish on Github</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h3 id="using-rake-tasks">Using Rake tasks</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Create a new page: <code>rake page name="contact.md"</code></li>
  <li>Create a new post: <code>rake post title="TITLE OF THE POST"</code></li>
</ul>

